ComicInfo.Summary:
The Cal Files, Part 1: Judge Edgar has Judge Dredd investigate the tampering of files originally belonging to insane Chief Judge Cal.
The Old Straight Track, Part 6: Luke and Zeke are attacked by village creatures.
Case Nine: Spear Of Destiny: The story on how the Spear of Destiny ended up in the hands of Adolf Hitler and later, the staff to hold the American flag on the Moon landing.
Lord of Misrule, Part 2: Slaíne is reincarnated as Robin as he tries to find out the name of the sword of the blood god from Niamh, reincarnated as Sister Marian.
Maniac 6, Part 4: Maniac 6 fights Maniac 5.
Bad Frendz, Part 5: Judge Dredd captures Dance.
